				</div>
				<!-- contact -->
    	        <hr />
				<h2>Staying in Touch with Seattle Vipassana</h2>
				<div class="spacedParas">
					<p>Sign up to receive email updates about activities at SVH, announcements of spontaneous same-day group sittings (known as "flash sits"), and other Vipassana events in the Seattle area, at <a href="http://www.kunja.dhamma.org/os/Subscription.html">http://www.kunja.dhamma.org/os/Subscription.html</a><p>
					<p>Join us on Facebook at <a href="https://www.facebook.com/dhammakunja">https://www.facebook.com/dhammakunja</a></p>
					<p>Questions about the Seattle Vipassana Hall can be sent to <a href="mailto:info-seattle@kunja.dhamma.org">info-seattle@kunja.dhamma.org</a></p>
				</div>
				<!-- donate -->
    	        <hr />
				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
