					<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-right:20px">
        	        	<h2>Donate to SVH</h2>
            	    	<p>Rent and other expenses for the Seattle Vipassana Hall total about $1,375 per month. If you are interested in supporting the Seattle Vipassana Hall with a tax-deductible donation, please select an option from the sidebar to the right. Or, if you prefer, you can use online banking or mail a check payable to <i>Northwest Vipassana Association</i> to the following address:</p>
                		<p style="padding: 5px 0 5px 150px;">Seattle Vipassana Hall<br />
                  											1800 Westlake Ave. N., Suite 301<br />
                  											Seattle, WA 98109</p>
					</td>
