				<!-- directions -->
    	        <hr />
                <h2>Driving Directions and Site Details</h2>
				<p>The Seattle Vipassana Hall is located at 1800 Westlake Ave. N., Suite 301, Seattle, WA 98109, in a commercial building overlooking Lake Union.  Map and directions <a href="http://mapq.st/kC69xp" target="_blank">http://mapq.st/kC69xp</a>. There is plenty of free parking on evenings and weekends. Bicycle parking is available only at the bike rack in front of the building just north of the Vipassana Hall. Metro Transit provides service to Westlake Ave. N., please check <a href="http://metro.kingcounty.gov/" target="_blank">their website</a> for updated route information. On Saturdays and Sundays, the building can only be entered through the North end door, at street level.  The Seattle Vipassana Hall is upstairs, in Suite 301.</p>
				
